{"tid":1938172,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[有用post/轉貼] 時事台手足呢段分析好值得我地驚惕","createTime":"2020-03-22T11:06:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T17:32:16.000Z","uid":76115,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"019a652e1840e53b66c45978c7a6537bc180eedc","tid":1938172,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T11:06:02.000Z","msg":"何謂五毛 ？<br />\n一般大家覺得五毛就係收錢做打手嘅賤種，但我發現呢個分析框架已經唔再適用，所以我會提倡將五毛分為以下兩種：<br />\n收費五毛：即係網絡打手，係有收錢而且有組織咁製造輿論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其中包括PR公司、中共網軍、任何收錢帶風向嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n免費五毛：冇錯佢哋係冇收錢，但客觀做嘅嘢同收錢五毛冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其中包括真心膠、假膠、Mon post狗、被帶風向嘅手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解會有所謂免費五毛？係因為連登（高登）嘅獨有文化 &ndash; 玩膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n玩膠即係無厘頭或不合邏輯咁惡搞或戲虐某人或某事，例如<strong>專登打錯字、打表情符號、誇張失實嘅標題、冇道德底線嘅言論</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢班玩膠嘅人主要會喺<strong>體育台（波台）、娛樂台、感情台</strong>出沒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong>經常會出post同回覆，目的就係引人注意，獲得最多嘅正負評、回覆</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原本係高登留落嚟嘅文化，但我覺得依家係有俾收費五毛利用去隱藏身份打輿論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1937824/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1937824/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n留意到Kpop台尤其係紅字嗰班好多都中哂粗體段落所講嘅野<br />\n色狗性癮post、吹捧護旗idol、圖文不相符脫離現實等等<br />\n我開始懷疑Kpop娛台喺我地唔留意下已經逐啲畀VR公司滲透緊, 希望大家真係要留意下"},{"pid":"11fb837feeda69f29f52c8b5e160de9efe34bc0d","tid":1938172,"uid":193951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T11:08:59.000Z","msg":"5能系牙-.-"},{"pid":"de36e22bf2dc2eb642a6be1265bb1aa3d56e0f46","tid":1938172,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"11fb837feeda69f29f52c8b5e160de9efe34bc0d","tid":1938172,"uid":193951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T11:08:59.000Z","msg":"5能系牙-.-"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T11:10:13.000Z","msg":"又block一件"},{"pid":"f5cb9b9151ef91b923d8ba8a255f8e82f8700f50","tid":1938172,"uid":96439,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T11:11:28.000Z","msg":"CC台可以開核彈post呃rate<br />\n波台玩膠就係免費五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"953531c14d4c01ff5fcf0954cc4df8908a22895d","tid":1938172,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de36e22bf2dc2eb642a6be1265bb1aa3d56e0f46","tid":1938172,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"11fb837feeda69f29f52c8b5e160de9efe34bc0d","tid":1938172,"uid":193951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T11:08:59.000Z","msg":"5能系牙-.-"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T11:10:13.000Z","msg":"又block一件"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T11:14:57.000Z","msg":"block咗好耐啦"},{"pid":"fdda121e129b622e9453f1a4d94c800f0c67e7ae","tid":1938172,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T11:19:49.000Z","msg":"我俾人點左名做五毛，但明明我個  post 係開係感情台 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多人討論唔小心上左熱門啫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2555f4709034f39b0949dc3272e8edc1c90dc2d","tid":1938172,"uid":165368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T11:33:44.000Z","msg":"我上次個名有括弧被人屈5毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"551a09aca33a9621db96fdbdb6324f4cb7b9f0cc","tid":1938172,"uid":87394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2555f4709034f39b0949dc3272e8edc1